      <p><b>Page 86</b>. The F-beta measure presented in Chapter 4 was
      first intoduced in Jardine, N. and van Rijsbergen, C.J., 'The
      use of hierarchic clustering in information retrieval',
      <i>Information Storage and Retrieval</i>, <b>7</b>, 217-240
      (1971). This reference is missing in the book.</p> 
